GC-content of splicing factors and their splicing targets

Things I did

  • Aligned raw data from Rogalska et al. of 305 splicing factors KD
  • Detected alternative splicing events with rMATS
  • Extracted exon skipping/inclusion events
  • Calculated GC/GC3% of these exons (only annotated exons with known CDS for now)
